Find your skin's best serum
This silky serum utilizes the proprietary Restor8™ Complex to address eight signs of aging: wrinkles and sagging skin, dehydration and lack of volume, dullness and uneven pigmentation, roughness and enlarged pores. A sophisticated concentration of Vitamins, Nutrients, Peptides, and Antioxidants helps to smooth and firm, moisturize and plump, even out skin tone, and refine texture.
Restor8™ is a proprietary complex of rare ingredients that produces a wide array of anti-aging benefits, including:

dramatically diminishing the appearance of expression lines and firming sagging skin;
enhancing the skin’s lipid moisture barrier and locking in essential hydration to plump up skin;
improving the skin's reflective ability in order to mask skin imperfections, while reducing redness and dark spots; 
smoothing skin and evening out texture and tone. 
Oil-free formula is ideal for all skin types. 


Available exclusively at Kate Somerville, Neiman Marcus and Bergdorf Goodman.
